quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,"And/by the strangers/life extractors , exaggerating/absorbing (violently)"
  79,2,"And/by the active/pullers , actively/pulling"
  79,3,"And/by the ships/stars/fast (could be angels), tending to the livelihood/floating"
  79,4,"So the racing/surpassing/preceding, racing/surpassing/preceding"
  79,5,So the regulators/arrangers/planners (of) a matter/affair/order/command
  79,6,A day/time the first blow of the horn trembles and shakes/agitates
  79,7,The followed closely behind follows it
  79,8,Hearts (on) that day (are) palpitating/pounding
  79,9,Its eyesight/understanding (is) humble/submissive
  79,10,"They say: \"Are we returning (E) in the first creation"
  79,11,Is (it that) if we were decayed/decomposed bones
  79,12,"They said: \"That is then a loosing repetition"
  79,13,So but it is one deterrent/cry to drive out
  79,14,So then they are at the Earth`s surface
  79,15,Did Moses` information/speech come to you
  79,16,When His Lord called him at the Valley the Holy/Sanctified Tuwan/concealed/folded within
  79,17,"Go to Pharaoh, that he truly exceeded the limit/tyrannized"
  79,18,"So say: `Is there for you that (E) you purify/become righteous"
  79,19,And I guide you to your Lord so you fear
  79,20,"So he showed him/made him understand the verse/evidence/sign, the greatest/biggest"
  79,21,"So he denied/falsified , and he disobeyed"
  79,22,Then he gave his back/ended/passed hastening
  79,23,"So he gathered, so he called"
  79,24,"So he said: \"I am your lord the highest/mightiest"
  79,25,So God punished/took him (the) severe exemplary punishment (of) the end (other life) and the first/beginning
  79,26,That truly in that (is) an example/warning (E) to who fears